Use the standard library
This is how to max_element of l:
   Remember that best is item 0 in l
   Remember that n is l's length
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that x is item i in l
      When x is more than best, then:
         Remember that best is x
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is best
